        <mxCell id="s6" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=11;arcSize=8;" value="&lt;b&gt;Mobile App &amp;amp; Backend&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• RN + Expo (Library · Studio · Settings)&lt;br&gt;• Async job API (generate/structure/export)&lt;br&gt;• Accounts via external IdP (JWKS)&lt;br&gt;• Fly / VPS deployment">
